<td valign="top" width="86">\r\n<p align="center">E04</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="355">\r\n<p align="center">Assistant Manager (Signal and Telecom)  Noida - GR, Noida</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="112">\r\n<p align="center">07</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="86">\r\n<p align="center">NE01</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="355">\r\n<p align="center">Junior Engineer (Electrical)  Vijaywada / Mumbai / Noida - GR, Noida</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="112">\r\n<p align="center">57</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<strong><u>Age Limit</u></strong> (as on 01/01/2016): 18 to 28 years for all posts (i.e born not earlier than 02.01.88 and not later than 01.01.98)\r\n\r\n<strong><u>Pay Grade (IDA):</u></strong>\r\n\r\nAssistant Manager -&gt;  20600 - 46500/-\r\nJunior Engineer -&gt;  13500 - 25520/-\r\n\r\n<strong><u>Educational Qualifications:</u></strong>\r\n\r\nAssistant Manager (Electrical) -&gt; GATE qualified candidates for the year 2015 or 2016. Candidates should have secured minimum 60% marks or equivalent CGPA in B.E. / B.Tech (Electrical) from a Govt. recognized University / Institute, with a valid GATE Score in 2015 or 2016.\r\n\r\nAssistant Manager (Signal and Telecom) -&gt; GATE qualified candidates for the year 2015 or 2016. Candidates should have secured minimum 60% marks or equivalent CGPA in B.E. / B.Tech (Electronics) from a Govt. recognized University / Institute, with a valid GATE Score in 2015 or 2016.\r\n\r\nJunior Engineer (Electrical) -&gt; Three years Diploma in Electrical Engineering from Govt recognized Institute or equivalent.\r\n\r\n<strong><u>How to Apply:</u></strong> Engineering Graduates / Diploma Engineers are required to Apply Online through Delhi Metro Rail Online Portal. The Online Registration will start from 26th May 2016 (18:00 Hours onwards) and close on <u><strong>27/06/2016</strong></u> till 23:59 Hours.\r\n\r\n<u><strong>Important Dates</strong></u>:\r\n\r\