(102, 1, '2016-06-26 17:47:39', '2016-06-26 17:47:39', '<img class="alignleft  wp-image-98" src="http://findmynaukari.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/findmynaukari-rail.png" alt="findmynaukari rail" width="321" height="321" />\r\n\r\nNorth Central Railway College (NCRC), Tundla (Firozabad District, Uttar Pradesh State) Walk in Interview for engagement of Contract Basis Teachers on purely Part Time Contractual Basis. The last date for submission of applications is 18th July 2016.\r\n\r\n<u>Advertisement No.: NCRC/TDL/PGT/TGT/PRT/2016</u>\r\n<table border="1" width="596" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="173">\r\n<p align="center"><strong><u>Name of the Post</u></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="239">\r\n<p align="center"><strong><u>Total Vacancies</u></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="182">\r\n<p align="center"><strong><u>Consolidated Monthly Remuneration</u></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="173">\r\n<p align="center"><strong>Lecturer (PGT)</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="239">\r\n<p align="center">06 (Biology  01, English  01, Commerce  01, History + Civics  01, Mathematics  01, Geography  01)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="182">\r\n<p align="center"> 27,500/- Per Month</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="173">\r\n<p align="center"><strong>Assistant Teacher (TGT)</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="239">\r\n<p align="center">10 (Music / Vocal  01, PTI (Male)  01, English  01, Maths + Science  03, Social Science  01, English + Geography  01, Hindi + Sanskrit  01, Hindi + English  01)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="182">\r\n<p align="center"> 26,250/- Per Month</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="173">\r\n<p align="center"><strong>Primary Teacher (PRT)</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="239">\r\n<p align="center">11</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign="top" width="182">\r\n<p align="center"> 21,250/- Per Month</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<strong><u>Educational Qualifications:</u></strong>\r\n\r\nPGT -&gt;\r\n\r\n(1) Second Class Master Degree in respective discipline at graduation level from a recognized University with at least 50% in aggregate. (OR) Two years integrated Post Graduate M.Sc. Course of Regional College of Education of NCERT in the concerned subject with at least 50% marks in aggregate.\r\n(2) B.Ed, or equivalent Degree from recognized University.\r\n(3) Proficiency in Teaching, Hindi and English medium.\r\n(4) Desirable: Knowledge of Computer Applications.\r\n\r\nTGT -&gt;\r\n\r\n(1) Second Class Bachelor''s Degree in concerned discipline with at least 50% marks in aggregate. (OR) Four years integrated Degree course of Regional College of Education of NCERT in the concerned subjects with at least 50% marks in aggregate.\r\n(2) B.Ed, or equivalent Degree from recognized University.\r\n(3) Must be Qualified CTET/TET\r\n(4) Proficiency in Teaching, Hindi and English medium.\r\n(5) Desirable - Knowledge of Computer Applications.\r\n\r\nPRT -&gt;\r\n\r\n(1) Senior Secondary School Certificate with 50% marks in aggregate or Intermediate with 50% marks in aggregate or its equivalent.\r\n(2) Diploma or certificate in Basic Teacher''s Training of duration of not less than two years or B.Ed, or equivalent Degree from recognized University.\r\n(3) Must be Qualified CTET/TET.\r\n(4) Proficiency in Teaching. Hindi and English medium.\r\n(5) Desirable: Knowledge of Computer Application''s.\r\n\r\n<strong><u>Selection Process</u></strong>: Walk in Interview. The List of Eligible candidates for Interview will be displayed on College Notice Board on 9th August 2016.\r\n\r\n(a) The Interview for PGT on 11th August 2016 at 8:00 am,\r\n(b) The Interview for TGT on 12th August 2016 at 8:00 am &amp; (c) Interview\r\n(c) for PRT on 13thAugust 2016 at 8:00 am pm in Principal''s Chamber, NCR College, Tundla.\r\n\r\n<strong><u>How to Apply</u></strong>: Last date for submission of the application along with the Photostat copies duly attested through Registered Post under addressed to <u>PRINCIPAL, NORTH CENTRAL RAILWAY COLLEGE, TUNDLA DISTT FIROZABAD, PIN 283204, (UP)</u> is <u><strong>18/07/2016</strong></u>, Willing candidates are requested to submit their application for each post in separate envelope.\r\n<table border="1" width="321" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" width="319"><a class="external" title="Opens new window" href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/0Bz3xO6e_7OeeXzh5eUx4TzhvTFE/" target="_blank">NCRC Advertisement with Application Form &gt;&gt;</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nRead more:', 'North Central Railway College Tundla Recruitment 2016 Contract Teachers (27 Vacancies)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'north-central-railway-college-tundla-recruitment-2016-contract-teachers-27-vacancies', '', '', '2016-06-26 17:47:39', '2016-06-26 17:47:39', '', 0, 'http://findmynaukari.com/?p=102', 0, 'post', '', 0),
